snippet.title: Synergy - Official Full Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Synergy leaves Early Access on April 16! 🌿

Get ready for a brand-new campaign with three scenarios, new buildings & plants, a revamped exploration system and more!

Watch our new trailer and prepare for v1.0 on Steam, GOG and Epic Games Store!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1989070/Synergy/

#synergy #gaming #citybuilder #indiegame
